name: customsearch
title: CustomSearch API
description: Searches over a website or collection of websites

fields.description: Selector specifying which fields to include in a partial response.

key.description: API key. Your API key identifies your project and provides you with API access, quota, and reports. Required unless you provide an OAuth 2.0 token.

oauth_token.description: OAuth 2.0 token for the current user.

prettyPrint.description: Returns response with indentations and line breaks.

quotaUser.description: An opaque string that represents a user for quota purposes. Must not exceed 40 characters.

list.description: Returns metadata about the search performed, metadata about the custom search engine used for the search, and the search results. Uses a small set of url patterns.

c2coff.description: Turns off the translation between zh-CN and zh-TW.

cx.description: The custom search engine ID to scope this search query

dateRestrict.description: Specifies all search results are from a time period

exactTerms.description: Identifies a phrase that all documents in the search results must contain

excludeTerms.description: Identifies a word or phrase that should not appear in any documents in the search results

fileType.description: Returns images of a specified type. Some of the allowed values are: bmp, gif, png, jpg, svg, pdf, ...

filter.description: Controls turning on or off the duplicate content filter.

googlehost.description: The local Google domain to use to perform the search.

highRange.description: Creates a range in form as_nlo value..as_nhi value and attempts to append it to query

hq.description: Appends the extra query terms to the query.

imgColorType.description: Returns black and white, grayscale, or color images: mono, gray, and color.

imgDominantColor.description: Returns images of a specific dominant color: red, orange, yellow, green, teal, blue, purple, pink, white, gray, black and brown.

imgSize.description: Returns images of a specified size, where size can be one of: icon, small, medium, large, xlarge, xxlarge, and huge.

imgType.description: Returns images of a type, which can be one of: clipart, face, lineart, news, and photo.

linkSite.description: Specifies that all search results should contain a link to a particular URL

lowRange.description: Creates a range in form as_nlo value..as_nhi value and attempts to append it to query

lr.description: The language restriction for the search results

num.description: Number of search results to return

orTerms.description: Provides additional search terms to check for in a document, where each document in the search results must contain at least one of the additional search terms

relatedSite.description: Specifies that all search results should be pages that are related to the specified URL

rights.description: Filters based on licensing. Supported values include: cc_publicdomain, cc_attribute, cc_sharealike, cc_noncommercial, cc_nonderived and combinations of these.

enumDescriptions: Enables highest level of safe search filtering.

siteSearch.description: Specifies all search results should be pages from a given site

siteSearchFilter.description: Controls whether to include or exclude results from the site named in the as_sitesearch parameter

sort.description: The sort expression to apply to the results

start.description: The index of the first result to return
